---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const data = {
  title: "Matrixezz: Your Complete Matrix Theorem Calculator",
  description: `Matrixezz es un proyecto colaborativo que desarrollé como Backend specialist junto a mi colega Frontend, Angel. Esta aplicación resuelve teoremas de matrices de álgebra lineal a nivel universitario, diseñada específicamente para las necesidades de nuestra clase.`,
  features: [
    "Comprehensive Functionality: Handles basic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and scalar multiplication, along with advanced 'compound' methods such as Gauss, Gauss-Jordan, and Classic Inverse Matrix calculations. It also provides determinant and transpose functionalities.",
    "Step-by-Step Solutions: For complex operations like Gauss and Gauss-Jordan, Matrixezz offers a unique 'Add steps' feature, providing a detailed guide to the solution process.",
    "Robust Architecture: Built with a classic Frontend-Backend architecture utilizing HTML, CSS (SCSS), and Vanilla JavaScript on the client side, and a Java, Spring Boot, and Maven backend. All heavy matrix calculations are efficiently handled on the server.",
    "User-Friendly & Secure: The intuitive UI is complemented by robust security protocols on both the client and server sides, including flags for locked matrices, process inclusion, fatal errors/incorrect rule usage, and missing data, ensuring accurate results and a smooth user experience."
  ],
  duration: "2 months",
  deployment: "Java executable",
  github: "https://github.com/angellvsdev/Matrixezz",
  images: [
    "/projects/matrixezz/determinant.png",
    "/projects/matrixezz/gaus_jordan.png",
    "/projects/matrixezz/gaus_method.png"
  ],
  videos: [
    "/projects/matrixezz/demonstration.mp4"
  ]
};
---

<Layout>
<div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 py-12 px-4 md:px-0 transition-colors duration-500">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-center text-center animate-fadein">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 drop-shadow mb-2">Calculadora de Teoremas de Matrices - Matrixezz</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 mb-4">{data.description}</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center mb-2">
        <span class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-950 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold shadow-sm">Java</span>
        <span class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-950 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold shadow-sm">Spring Boot</span>
        <span class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-950 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold shadow-sm">Maven</span>
        <span class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-950 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold shadow-sm">JavaScript puro</span>
        <a href={data.github} target="_blank" class="bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold shadow-sm hover:underline transition">Repositorio</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-10 animate-fadein-up">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" /></svg>
        Características y enfoque
      </h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 space-y-2">
        <li>Funcionalidad completa: Opera suma, resta, multiplicación y multiplicación por escalar, además de métodos avanzados como Gauss, Gauss-Jordan e Inversa clásica. También calcula determinantes y transpuestas.</li>
        <li>Soluciones paso a paso: Para operaciones complejas como Gauss y Gauss-Jordan, Matrixezz ofrece una función única de “Agregar pasos”, guiando el proceso detalladamente.</li>
        <li>Arquitectura robusta: Frontend con HTML, SCSS y JavaScript puro; backend en Java, Spring Boot y Maven. Todos los cálculos se procesan en el servidor para máxima eficiencia.</li>
        <li>Interfaz amigable y segura: UI intuitiva y protocolos de seguridad en cliente y servidor, con banderas para matrices bloqueadas, inclusión de procesos, errores fatales y datos faltantes para garantizar resultados precisos.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-10 animate-fadein-up delay-100">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" /></svg>
        Detalles del proyecto
      </h2>
      <ul class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Duración:</strong> 2 meses</li>
        <li><strong>Despliegue:</strong> Ejecutable Java</li>
        <li><strong>Repositorio:</strong> <a href={data.github} target="_blank" class="text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 underline hover:opacity-80">{data.github}</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-10 animate-fadein-up delay-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" /></svg>
        Galería
      </h2>
      <div class="matrixezz-gallery grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <img src="/projects/matrixezz/determinant.png" alt="Cálculo del determinante en Matrixezz" class="rounded-lg shadow-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-full h-auto object-contain transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/projects/matrixezz/gaus_jordan.png" alt="Método Gauss-Jordan en Matrixezz" class="rounded-lg shadow-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-full h-auto object-contain transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/projects/matrixezz/gaus_method.png" alt="Método de Gauss en Matrixezz" class="rounded-lg shadow-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-full h-auto object-contain transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900" loading="lazy" />
        <video src="/projects/matrixezz/demostration.mp4" controls class="rounded-lg shadow-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-full h-auto object-contain bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 cursor-pointer" style="max-height:350px"></video>
      </div>
      <script type="module" src="/src/pages/proyectos/MatrixezzModal.js"></script>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-10 animate-fadein-up delay-300">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-700 dark:text-pink-300 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-pink-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" /></svg>
        ¿Cómo funciona?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 leading-relaxed">
        Matrixezz está construido con una arquitectura clásica de Frontend y Backend. El frontend fue desarrollado por Angel utilizando HTML, SCSS y JavaScript puro, mientras que yo (Reny) me encargué del backend en Java con Spring Boot y Maven. Todos los cálculos de matrices se procesan en el servidor para garantizar eficiencia y seguridad. La interfaz es intuitiva y robusta, con manejo detallado de errores y soluciones paso a paso para los teoremas avanzados.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a href="/" class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 bg-blue-700 dark:bg-blue-400 text-white dark:text-slate-900 px-5 py-3 rounded-full shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-blue-800 dark:hover:bg-blue-300 transition-all focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 animate-fadein-up" title="Volver al inicio" aria-label="Volver al inicio">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l9-9 9 9M4 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11v11a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3" /></svg>
    Inicio
  </a>

  <style>
    .animate-fadein {
      animation: fadein 1s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) both;
    }
    .animate-fadein-up {
      animation: fadein-up 0.8s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) both;
    }
    .animate-fadein-up.delay-100 { animation-delay: .1s; }
    .animate-fadein-up.delay-200 { animation-delay: .2s; }
    .animate-fadein-up.delay-300 { animation-delay: .3s; }
    @keyframes fadein {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }
    @keyframes fadein-up {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
  </style>
</div>
</Layout>
